parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Pump Control Module Failure due to Condensation and Water Ingress
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump control module can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down while driving, leading to potential accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
the "Drivetrain Malfunction" warning appears on the dashboard
the vehicle jerks or shakes before coming to a complete stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unpredictable jerking and locking of the steering wheel can cause the vehicle to swerve or lose control, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The steering wheel jerks or locks suddenly
causing the vehicle to swerve or lose control
especially when driving on the highway or navigating turns or potholes. In some cases
the brakes may not function properly
making it difficult to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Drivetrain Malfunction Warning and Reduced Output
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The drivetrain malfunction warning can cause a reduction in drivetrain output, leading to decreased vehicle performance and potentially affecting the vehicle's ability to accelerate or maintain speed, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Drivetrain malfunction warning on the instrument display
reduced drivetrain output
instrument cluster malfunction or failure
high voltage battery not fully charged when driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate charging of the high voltage battery can lead to reduced vehicle performance, decreased fuel efficiency, and potentially cause drivetrain malfunctions, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: High voltage battery not fully charged when driving
drivetrain malfunction warning
reduced drivetrain output.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to overheat, leading to costly repairs, engine damage, and potentially causing the vehicle to stall or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine overheats
the temperature gauge rises
coolant leaks
the water pump fails
the serpentine belt breaks or wears out prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the serpentine belt can cause the engine to overheat, leading to costly repairs, engine damage, and potentially causing the vehicle to stall or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The serpentine belt breaks
cracks
or wears out prematurely
the engine overheats
the temperature gauge rises
the power steering fails
the alternator fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the passenger restraint system can lead to false warnings, which can be distracting and annoying, and may also affect the proper functioning of the airbag system, potentially compromising passenger safety.
symptoms: The passenger restraint system warning light comes on when someone sits on the passenger seat
the warning light comes on even when no one is sitting on the passenger seat
the seatbelt warning is always on even when no one is sitting on the passenger seat
the car produces noisy alarms telling the driver to buckle the seatbelt on the passenger seat when driving alone.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the passenger restraint system to malfunction, leading to false warnings and potentially affecting the proper deployment of airbags in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger restraint system warning light comes on
the airbag sensor needs to be replaced
the replacement sensor is faulty and needs to be reordered.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The poor service experience can lead to frustration and inconvenience for the vehicle owner, and may also affect their trust in the dealership and the manufacturer.
symptoms: The dealership fails to communicate effectively with the owner
the dealership takes a long time to diagnose and repair the issue
the dealership fails to provide a functional replacement part
the owner is told that they will have to pay for the service and replacement after the warranty ends.
